<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Problem Information</title>
    <!--<script type="text/javascript" src="/static/js/tools.js"></script>-->
    <script
		  src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.1.1.min.js"
		  integrity="sha256-hVVnYaiADRTO2PzUGmuLJr8BLUSjGIZsDYGmIJLv2b8="
		  crossorigin="anonymous">
    </script>
    <script
      src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/js/bootstrap.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-Tc5IQib027qvyjSMfHjOMaLkfuWVxZxUPnCJA7l2mCWNIpG9mGCD8wGNIcPD7Txa"
      crossorigin="anonymous">
    </script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/clipboard.js/1.5.16/clipboard.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/static/js/ace-min/ace.js" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/static/css/auth/signup.css">
    <script src="/static/js/auth/signup.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-default navbar-fixed-top">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="navbar-header">
          <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbar" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="navbar">
            <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          </button>
          <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Judge</a>
        </div>
        <div id="navbar" class="collapse navbar-collapse">
          <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
            <li><a href="/problems"><%=__("problems")%></a></li>
            <li><a href="/result"><%=__("submitHistory")%></a></li>
            <li><a href="/rank"><%=__("rank")%></a></li>
            <li><a href="#"><%=__("contests")%></a></li>
          </ul>
          <%- include ./../topbar-right.ejs %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="container" id="div-content">
      <div class="row" id="div-spacer-top">
      </div>
    </div>
    <% if(typeof myid=="undefined" || myid==null) { %>
      <div class="container" id="div-signup-container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="panel panel-default" id="panel-tos">
            <div class="panel-heading">
              <h3 class="panel-title"><%=__("tos")%></h3>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aenean ultricies, arcu id vestibulum feugiat, libero augue gravida lorem, feugiat dictum arcu augue at ante. Praesent ultricies est metus, id rutrum neque porttitor ut. Phasellus ut urna et diam blandit tincidunt nec ut purus. Integer nec efficitur velit. Vivamus elementum est sed velit pretium consectetur. Nunc luctus, dolor a aliquam fermentum, nibh diam vestibulum nibh, ac maximus ex tortor hendrerit felis. Nunc vitae sagittis ligula, ut blandit odio. Sed ante massa, ultricies ut augue mollis, laoreet sodales leo.
            </div>
          </div>
            <input id="input-tos-agree" type="checkbox" name="tos_agree" value="1"><%=__("agreeTOS")%><br>
            <p class="p-error text-danger" id="p-error-tos"></p>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div style="padding-top: 15px; padding-bottom: 15px;"><%-__("mandatoryNoti")%></div>
          <div class="input-group input-signup">
            <span class="input-group-addon" id="sizing-addon"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-user text-info"></span></span>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="<%=__("username")%>" aria-describedby="sizing-addon2" id="input-id">
          </div>
          <%=__("signupIDLimits")%>
          <p class="p-error text-danger" id="p-error-id"></p>
          <div class="input-group input-signup">
            <span class="input-group-addon" id="sizing-addon"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-lock text-info"></span></span>
            <input type="password" class="form-control" placeholder="<%=__("password")%>" aria-describedby="sizing-addon2" id="input-pw">
          </div>
          <%=__("signupPWLimits")%>
          <p class="p-error text-danger" id="p-error-pw"></p>
          <div class="input-group input-signup">
            <span class="input-group-addon" id="sizing-addon"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-lock text-info"></span></span>
            <input type="password" class="form-control" placeholder="<%=__("passwordAgain")%>" aria-describedby="sizing-addon2" id="input-pwagain">
          </div>
          <p class="p-error text-danger" id="p-error-pwagain"></p>
          <div class="input-group input-signup">
            <span class="input-group-addon" id="sizing-addon"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-envelope text-info"></span></span>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="<%=__("email")%>" aria-describedby="sizing-addon2" id="input-email">
          </div>
          <p class="p-error text-danger" id="p-error-email"></p>
          <div class="input-group input-signup">
            <span class="input-group-addon" id="sizing-addon"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-star"></span></span>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="<%=__("nickSameAsUsername")%>" aria-describedby="sizing-addon2" id="input-nickname">
          </div>
          <%=__("canChangeAfterSignUp")%>
          <p class="p-error text-danger" id="p-error-nickname"></p>
          <div class="input-group input-signup">
            <span class="input-group-addon" id="sizing-addon"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-tree-deciduous"></span></span>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="<%=__("org")%>" aria-describedby="sizing-addon2" id="input-org">
          </div>
          <p class="p-error text-danger" id="p-error-org"></p>
        </div>
        <div class="row" id="div-btn-submit">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-success" id="btn-submit"><%=__("submit")%></button>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% } else { %>
      <div class="container" id="div-signup-container">
        <div class="row" id="div-login">
          <div class="page-header"><h2>Already logged in!</h2></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% } %>
    <%- include footer.ejs %>
  </body>
</html>
